text: Sooner or Sooners may refer to: * Sooners, early Oklahoma, US settlers ** Oklahoma Sooners, University of Oklahoma varsity sports teams named after the early settlers * Ottawa Sooners, Canadian football team in Ontario * 18876 Sooner, asteroid * A Girl Named Sooner, a 1975 TV movie ==See also== * * * Sooner or Later (disambiguation) * The Sooner It Comes, album by Aloud * Schooner (disambiguation)
